## Order Types Color Coding

```
BUY / LONG entry:  #00d4a8
SELL / SHORT entry: #ff4d6a
LIMIT pending:      #f59e0b (amber — waiting)
MARKET:             #60a8ff (blue — instant)
SL order active:    #ff8c42 (orange — protective)
CANCELLED:          #3a4d60 (dimmed out)
COMPLETE:           #00d4a8 for buy, #ff4d6a for sell
```

