## Status Bar

```
Market OPEN:     #00d4a8
Market CLOSED:   #3a4d60
API CONNECTED:   #00d4a8 dot
API ERROR:       #ff4d6a dot
Heartbeat tick:  #2a3a50 / #00d4a8 alternating (subtle pulse)
```

